name: Pixel Nebula
description: A dreamy pixel cloud from a retro-futuristic galaxy! Pixel Nebula pixelates market chaos into cute 8-bit charts, auto-hunts yields in virtual farms, protects against hacks with glitch shields, and upgrades your agent life with sparkly updates. Float through the blockchain cosmos in low-res rainbow bliss!
